                    and <m>\mathbf{Z(5, 3)}</m>. On the same axes, plot <m>\mathbf{X'Y'Z'}</m>, 
                    the image of triangle <m>\mathbf{XYZ}</m> under a translation given by <m>\binom{4}{9}.</m>
                </p>
            </statement>
        </exercise>
